  "description": "A breathtaking sunset over a body of water, with a silhouetted landscape of mountains and trees in the foreground. The sky is ablaze with vibrant colors, transitioning from deep reds and oranges near the horizon to lighter hues of orange and yellow higher up. Wispy clouds are illuminated by the setting sun, creating a dramatic and textured effect. Below, a lush green canopy of trees occupies the lower portion of the frame. A hint of city lights can be seen in the distant valley. The overall composition is a wide, panoramic view, capturing the expansive beauty of nature.",
